{
  "stem": "23350.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they couldn't eat, and every time, they said, send it to Minia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they had so much pity for me, I was so thin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They couldn't eat anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't want it, because I knew they need it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But no, they were already really dying already, they knew they were, and they didn't want it, and they couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they sent it to me so I should survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one night, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Chanke, ?] she was such a beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "These two girls, they were so sad-- I mean, the Germans were so sadistic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They left some girls with long hair, and some-- and most of us were shaved, so that we can see what somebody looks like with hair.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this girl, this [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Chanke, ?] had this most beautiful, natural hair, till here, beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she had-- she got pneumonia, actually, and she didn't look-- it didn't-- well, there was no medicine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one day, she developed a very, very high temperature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then they isolated her, put her into another place, because she was very contagious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one night-- and I dreamt about her that night, it's really amazing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the morning, they told me that [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Chanke ?] died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's amazing, things which were happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the other girl was coughing and coughing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was also very ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was-- And in 1944, in February, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were sent to-- on the open trains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were going-- one morning, we started very early, travelling all day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we would be travelling all night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We came back on the same place where we started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They let us out down in the fields, just to do our business.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
